title: Wexford Carol (Jon Schmidt Christmas) The Piano Guys
description:
Dive into the enchanting melodies of "Wexford Carol," a gem from the rich treasury of Irish Christmas music. Originating from County Wexford, this ancient carol is one of the oldest surviving Christmas songs in Europe, echoing through the ages with its hauntingly beautiful tune and reflective lyrics. Its deep roots in Irish tradition bring a touch of historical charm to your holiday season. As you listen, let the timeless magic of "Wexford Carol" transport you to a bygone era of yuletide cheer and profound tranquility.

title: North Pole Express - Ding Dong Merrily On High (Winter Serenade) The Piano Guys
description:
Welcome aboard the festive journey with "North Pole Express (Ding Dong Merrily On High)"! This cheerful carol set in the playful 5/4 time signature brings a fresh twist of joy and jingles to your Christmas playlist. Fun fact: while we've playfully borrowed 'North Pole Express' from our favorite holiday train adventure (no hard feelings, Polar Express!), our song promises a unique sleigh ride of melodies and merriment. So, buckle up your sleigh belts and get ready to ride the rails with us! 🎄🔔🚂
